'''Summer Festival Jam 2025''' is a summer-themed [[Avatars|avatar]] jam, which is a continuation of the previously named [[Summer Music Fest Jam]]. It took take place from August 1, 2025 to August 15, 2025.

==Details==
===Dates===
Submissions for the jam began on June 23 and closed on July 21. Submissions were judged from July 21 to July 31. Winners of the jam were be announced on August 1, along with group events hosted in collaboration with the jam.

===Theme===
The theme of this avatar jam is summer, more specifically:

{{Quote|We’re looking for avatars that emphasize “summer vibes at the beach,” whatever that may mean to you!<ref>[https://ask.vrchat.com/t/summer-festival-jam-2025-june-23-july-21-2025/44710 Summer Festival Jam 2025 - June 23 - July 21 2025]</ref>}}

Submissions were be judged in the follow categories:

{{Quote|Summer Vibe-iness - How well does this represent a “Summer Vibe”?

Overall Style - Is this really fashionable and appealing to users?

Performance Rank - Is this avatar Medium or better?

Extra Features - Does it have extra toggles for customization? Does it have additional features, such as face-tracking?
}}

====Requirements====
In addition to the general theme, submissions must follow these requirements:
* Avatar must be uploaded after the start of the jam
* Avatar height should be around 152cm - 180cm
* Avatar must be performance rank Medium or better.
* Avatar must have PC, Android, and iOS versions

To see the full list of requirements, see [https://ask.vrchat.com/t/summer-festival-jam-2025-june-23-july-21-2025/44710#p-81661-some-extra-important-avatar-requirements-3 here] and [https://hello.vrchat.com/summer-festival-jam-2025-rules here] for full contest details.

===Prizes===
The 12 winners of the jam of received the following:
* 1 year of [[VRC+]] (can be split with up to 4 people, if you worked on a team)
* An exclusive [[Badges|badge]]
* Fast-tracked into the [[Avatar Marketplace]] Sellers Program
* Avatar will be added in the [[Public Avatars|Public avatar row]]
* Opportunity to submit a single Avatar (purchasable or public) to be featured in the special Summer Festival row

